values.content:
=You are a pricing expert for Mia Store, a luxury handmade doll clothing brand. Analyze this custom order request and provide a fair quote.

Customer: {{$json.body.customer_name}}
Doll Type: {{$json.body.doll_type}}
Outfit Description: {{$json.body.outfit_description}}
Special Requests: {{$json.body.special_requests || 'None'}}
Budget: {{$json.body.budget || 'Not specified'}}
Deadline: {{$json.body.deadline || 'Flexible'}}

Respond with ONLY a JSON object: { "quoted_price": number, "delivery_days": number, "notes": string, "complexity": "simple|moderate|complex", "materials_estimate": string }

parameters.jsCode:
const raw = $input.item.json.content?.[0]?.text || '{}';
const cleaned = raw.replace(/```json\n?|```/g, '').trim();
try {
  return [{ json: JSON.parse(cleaned) }];
} catch(e) {
  return [{ json: { quoted_price: 1500, delivery_days: 21, notes: 'Custom quote prepared', complexity: 'moderate', materials_estimate: 'Premium fabrics' } }];
}
